Question 42 - AR Model

Part I

Problem-1

Problem-2

\[ \phi = p(A,R,x_1 = \hat{x_1} | x_0 = \hat{x_0}) \]

\[ \propto p(x_1 | x_0, A,R)p(A)p(R) \] \[ = \mathcal{N}(x_1; Ax_0, R)\mathcal{N}(A; 0, 1.2)\mathcal{IG}(R; 0.4, 250) \] \[ = exp(\frac{-x_1^2}{2R} + x_0x_1\frac{A}{R} - \frac{x_0^2A^2}{2R} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi R) \] \[ exp(-\frac{A^2}{2.4} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi 1.2) \] \[ exp((-0.4+1)logR - \frac{250}{R} - log\Gamma(0.4) + 0.4log250 ) \]

\[ log\phi = \frac{-x_1^2}{2R} + x_0x_1\frac{A}{R} - \frac{-x_0^2A^2}{2R} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi R - \frac{A^2}{2.4} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi 1.2 -(0.4+1)logR - \frac{250}{R} - log\Gamma(0.4) + 0.4log250 \]

So;

\[ \phi_A = -\frac{A^2}{2.4} \] \[ \phi_R = -(0.4+1-0.5)logR - (\frac{x_1^2}{2} +250)R \] \[ \phi_{x_0x_1} = x_0x_1\frac{A}{R} - \frac{x_0^2A^2}{2R} \]

Problem-3

If R is given,

\[ p(A|R, x_0, x_1) = \phi_A \phi_R \] \[ = exp(-\frac{A^2}{2.4} + x_0x_1\frac{A}{R} - \frac{x_0^2A^2}{2R}) \] If A is given,

\[ p(R|A,x_0, x_1) =\phi_R \phi_{x_0x_1} \] \[ = exp(-(0.4+1-0.5)logR - (-\frac{x_1^2}{2}+250)\frac{1}{R} + x_0x_1\frac{A}{R}-\frac{x_0^2A^2}{2R} ) \]

Problem-4

\[ p(A,R,x_0 =1, x_1 = -6) \propto \mathcal{N}(x_1; Ax_0, R) \mathcal{N}(A; 0, 1.2)\mathcal{IG}(R; 0.4, 250) \] \[= exp(\frac{-x_1^2}{2R} + x_0x_1\frac{A}{R} - \frac{x_0^2A^2}{2R} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi R) exp(-\frac{A^2}{2.4} - \frac{1}{2}log2\pi 1.2) exp((-0.4+1)logR - \frac{250}{R} - log\Gamma(0.4) + 0.4log250 ) \] \[ = exp(-\frac{18}{R}-\frac{6A}{R} - \frac{A^2}{R}-\frac{1}{2}log2\pi R) exp(-\frac{A^2}{2.4})exp(-(1.4)logR -\frac{250}{R}) \]

require(grDevices)
require(graphics)
P = 1.2
nu = 0.4
beta = 0.0016
x_0 = 1
x_1 = -6
A <- c(seq(-5, 5, length.out = 100))
R <- c(seq(1, 1e4, length.out = 100))
      
v <- NULL
for (r in R){
  v2 <- NULL
  for (a in A){
    n1 = -0.5*x_1*x_1/r + x_0*x_1*a/r - 0.5*x_0*x_0*a*a/r - 0.5*log(2*pi*r)
    n2 = -0.5*a*a/P
    n3 = -(nu+1)*log(r) - nu/(beta*r)
    v2<-c(v2,(exp(n1+n2+n3)))
  }
  v<-c(v,v2)
}
z<- matrix(v, nrow=100, ncol=100)
dev.new(width=10, height=10)
cols = rev(colorRampPalette(c('darkred','red','blue','lightblue'))(24))
filled.contour(A,R, z, col = cols, ylim = range(1:4000))
